{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bbb310d9ad","title":"对棉粮工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c9f1f07fd9","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ca5f2a4a7","type":"paragraph","text":"五一”节和张×的蓄","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"9becce79a3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月一日）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"41faf5058f","type":"paragraph","text":"五月一日晚上十点三十五分在天安门城楼上，江青同志向毛主席、林副主席单独引见了张×，接见时周总理也在座。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"bae55dcc60","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席、林副主席和张×亲切握手。毛主席红光满面，种朵奕爽，身体非常健康。这是中国人民和世界人民的最大幸福","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"883cae242b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青同志向毛主席，林付主席介绍说：这是国家科委张×，她们把韩光一伙打倒了，她们那里运动搞得不错。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"a9e0670c35","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说、应该祝科委同志们万寿无疆，应该就人民万寿无疆！毛主席又说：女同志也一样造反骤：你们把反革命韩光打倒了，你们夺权夺得好！接着主席又亲切地问，你现在担任什么工作张×同答说：在国家科委革命委员会工作。毛主席问：是革命委员会主任吧周总理说，也就是了吧这时，毛主席向林副主席说：她原来是个局长，和群众一起造反。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"43bde3a4ac","type":"paragraph","text":"对棉粮工作的指示","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"91637f8082","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月一日）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"1008d4e946","type":"paragraph","text":"必须把粮食抓紧，把锦花抓紧，把布正抓紧，粮油征腾工作不仅是一个经济任务，它首先是一个政治任务。一定要十分抓紧，每年-定要把收割、保管吃用（收、管、吃）抓的很紧，而且抓的及时。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"c989906a9a","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意储备，铺张浪费，吃光用光，这些都是错误的，都是粮食工作中的资产阶级反动路线或者是资产阶级思想的反映。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"ce537a18fe","type":"paragraph","text":"关于大批判题的指示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"606d96874d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年五月二日）","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"fcee5c5816","type":"paragraph","text":"批制文章不要象九评那样长，每篇一、二千字，不要超过三千字。一篇一个中心，一个概念，明明自白。长了就没有人看，记不住。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"77aa890480","type":"paragraph","text":"e809","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"page":{"id":"8d0a99dd63","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"bbb310d9ad","start":319,"end":319}},"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0061d0dd96","type":"title","text":"对棉粮工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"026e52b8c6","type":"paragraph","text":"必须把粮食抓紧，把棉花抓紧，把布匹抓紧，粮油征购工作不仅是一个经济任务，它首先是一个政治任务。一定要十分抓紧，每年一定要把收割、保管吃用（收、管、吃）抓得很紧，而且抓得及时。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"},{"id":"aa8d4be189","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意储备，铺张浪费，吃光用光，这些都是错误的，都是粮食工作中的资产阶级反动路线或者是资产阶级思想的反映","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad"}],"page":{"id":"53ed2fa5eb","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"bbb310d9ad","start":450,"end":450}}}},"__N_SSG":true}